              >
                Clarity for every episode.
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                Capture episodes in seconds, uncover patterns, and stay one step
                ahead. Clean, fast, and built for everyday use.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
                <a
